---
layout: base.njk
title: Clash for Windows 使用笔记 - 安装配置与场景文章
description: Clash for Windows 使用笔记汇集安装、配置、排错、下载与多平台场景文章。
permalink: /blog/
---
<section class="page-hero compact">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Blog</p>
    <h1>Clash for Windows 使用笔记</h1>
    <p>围绕安装、配置、版本整理、连接检查和多设备使用持续更新。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container layout-with-aside">
    <div class="article-list">
      {% for post in collections.postsByDate %}
      <article class="list-card">
        <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}文章配图" width="360" height="220" loading="lazy">
        <div>
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <div class="tag-row">
            {% for tag in post.data.tags | publicTags %}
            <a href="/tags/{{ tag | tagSlug }}/">{{ tag }}</a>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <aside class="side-panel">
      <h2>目录</h2>
      <a href="/blog/clash-for-windows-install-guide/">安装教程</a>
      <a href="/blog/clash-for-windows-profile-import/">配置导入</a>
      <a href="/blog/clash-for-windows-network-check/">连接检查</a>
      <a href="/download.html">下载中心</a>
      <h2>Tags</h2>
      <div class="tag-cloud">
        {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
        <a href="/tags/{{ tag | tagSlug }}/">{{ tag }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
